Package: gvalidatR
Title: enabling spreadsheet data entry, validation, and change management using git for research teams
Version: 0.0.0.9200
Authors@R: 
    person("Patrick", "Bills", , "billspat@msu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Enables data entry using Google sheets, rule-based validation based on data definitions, 
    and export into text-based CSV format for tracking changes to data using git.  designed to part
    of multiple git repositories (data/rules + analysis + synthesis) for meta analyses and following
    the data processing levels definitions of the Environmental Data Initiative (L0, L1, L2). 
